#ROOMS
#4000
At the Edge of the Cavern of Valshara~
A wide cavern stretches out to the south of you, framed between two guard 
towers, you can see the spires of the noble compounds behind the gate glowing
in faint purple faerie fire. To the north of you, the endless tunnels of the
wilds await. If you travel in that direction you are sure to find danger at 
least as great as any you would ever face upon the streets of valshara if 
not greater.
~
0 0 1 0 0 0 0 1000 0 0
