S
#4001
Within the Tunnels of the Wilds~
The walls around you are covered with phosphorencent fungus, just bright
enough to prevent easy use of infravision. You almost jump at shadows 
which seem to waver and move in the strange light. The wilds has a reputation
for being deadly, even drow have much to fear here.
~
